title: Days of our Lives Fri, Jun 28, 2013
description:
EJ begins his plan to bring down Stefano.


Sami worries when she realizes her case is much bleaker than she hoped.


Adrienne continues to argue with Justin over his decision to represent Sami. Justin accuses his wife of tearing apart their family.


Will is touched when he overhears Sonny defending him to Adrienne.


Jennifer is so angry with JJ she nearly falls apart. Later, JJ sees Jennifer and Daniel kissing and realizes how to use this to his advantage.
